# Rust formatting (CI)

GitHub Actions runs `cargo fmt --all --check` and fails if formatting is not up to date.

After editing any `*.rs` file, run:

```sh
cargo fmt --all
```

Before pushing or marking Rust work complete, verify:

```sh
cargo fmt --all --check
```

This is separate from tests. Keep the existing project rule that avoids long-running test commands.
